                    <div><p>Fairs, festivals, and events fill the annual calendar on Lond Island, New York. You and your friends can join the fun and participate in a number of activities. Learn about other cultures, enjoy food and drinks, or simply relax and enjoy the scene. Some of the annual festivals and events include:</p>
